lead_paragraph: Bobbi Kristina Brown's former boyfriend Nick Gordon has been wrongly targeted in the criminal probe of her 2015 death despite his efforts to save her life after finding her unresponsive in a bathtub in her Georgia home, his lawyers said on Tuesday.

headline.main: Bobbi Kristina Brown's Boyfriend Tried to Save Her Life-Lawyer
